Do you have any new book or production hmpp?

No book yet hahahah. I’m out every day until December, 4th. They’ll release a “Takash” doc (À Bas Delaporte Films) which we finished a couple of months ago. Apart from that the most ‘crazy’ news is the album (57) which is coming with Yuness Greenbaum’s feature and we’re actually working on the film PT.2, a Hyphen Hyphen x Asap Rocky video Clip that I produced and directed… which is a little well of my friendship wheel. Mura Masa came and recorded, KRAZI! …
